{"tid":1475760,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"短炒長遠必輸 - 數學解釋版","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:55:10.000Z","uid":87999,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a8b35cc72b8357ac0983145a55853abda34e2b6","tid":1475760,"uid":87999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"本金係100蚊 <br />\n期指又好, 股票又好啦,<br />\n如果贏左有150蚊, 輸左有50蚊<br />\n期望值expected value係 0.5*1.5+0.5*0.5=1 好似好公平<br />\n但計漏左複息效應 當某幾次連輸 輸到個本好細 就好難上番去<br />\n<br />\nrandom bet 7次會有呢幅圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hq4RGSu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhq4RGSu.png&h=14311fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果平均化左N次random bet , 就會發現個資本會越黎越細 <br />\n<br />\n牛熊, 期指更加衰, 升跌用點數係, 唔係百分比掛鉤, <br />\n贏左賺少d, 輸左輸多d"},{"pid":"d3b0adb4047191ec62ec5f3a94541d88ad03b242","tid":1475760,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:54:08.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f16c31b418e5e0114ae47b11249a8521c0bd3be6","tid":1475760,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmLA8zG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmLA8zG.jpg&h=58559c93&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQVUEGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQVUEGm.jpg&h=47f2c3d4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}